# Domain analyzer hardening exceptions.
#
# These aggregate/entity/value-object files use private constructors for EF Core
# materialization while public creation remains guarded by domain factories.
# Owner: Domain maintainers. Remove when the domain model no longer needs
# EF materialization constructors or uses constructor binding for these members.

